          "de": "!{{Schläft|Ist wach}}",
          "nl": "!{{Slaapt|Is wakker}}"
        },
        "hint": {
          "en": "Reflects the 'Asleep' sensor: set it via the 'Mark as asleep' flow action (e.g. in your bedtime routine); it switches to awake automatically when a freshly ended night's sleep syncs from Google Health.",
